data.description: Gorgeous two-story home in desired neighborhood. This large home features 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. Guest room on the main level, chef kitchen with lots of cabinets, granite countertops, breakfast area, pantry, and island. Large family room with fireplace. Formal living and dining rooms. Upstairs has a huge Owners Suite with a large walk-in closet, double vanity, garden tub, and shower. Loft area spacious additional bedrooms.
